          "params": [],
          "returnType": null,
          "description": "GLSL fragment shader source. Required. The shader receives these auto-bound uniforms: uniform sampler2D uTexture; // the filter's input uniform vec2 uResolution; // output dimensions And these auto-bound varyings: in vec2 vUv; // 0..1 across the quad"
